<h1>404 Screen Customization</h1>
<p>One can customize the 404 screen per realm. In order to do so please copy the global resource configuration</p>
<address>YANEL_HOME/src/webapp/global-resource-configs/404_yanel-rc.xml</address>
<p>into your realm</p>
<address>MY_REALM/src/webapp/global-resource-configs/</address>
<p>And start customizing this realm specific resource configuration</p>
<address>MY_REALM/src/webapp/global-resource-configs/404_yanel-rc.xml</address>
<p>An example can be found at</p>
<address>YANEL_HOME/src/realms/yanel-website/src/webapp/global-resource-configs/404_yanel-rc.xml</address>
</body></html>